Package: Earthquake
Type: Package
Title: A Set of Earthquake Mapping Geoms
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Joe Tapper
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: Josef Tapper <yourself@somewhere.net>
  This is a package containing several geoms for mapping earthquake data supplied by NOAA. 
  There are functions for preparing the data by tidying up the LOCATION_NAME 
  data and correcting for the BC year data. There are leaflet mapping functions, to  visualise 
  the locations of multiple earthquakes in a time window.
